<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The European pollock.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lob</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 5 ====
HEADWORD: Lob
<hw>Lob</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of lobbing;</def>
<specif>specif.,</specif> <def>an (often gentle) stroke which sends a
ball up into the air, as in tennis to avoid a player at the
net.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

